{"tid":388871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女朋友分開左半年，先睇清楚佢咩人","createTime":"2017-09-05T17:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T18:07:27.000Z","uid":142518,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0d75ba66a0dee24ce0b9965a0e1ac7b6764543","tid":388871,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"事源同ex一年前一齊<br />\n一齊期間佢對我好好<br />\n所以分開左都念念不忘<br />\n而且因為父母問題分開<br />\n所以一直以為有機會<br />\n<br />\n點知分開半年後<br />\n我同佢之前一齊識嘅女仔fd朋友A  <br />\nsend咗張圖比我<br />\n係我個ex wts同佢講話我地冇一齊過<br />\n仲話我呃個朋友A<br />\n<br />\n冇啦啦比朋友A話估吾到我呃佢<br />\n我都估吾到自己分開左半年先睇清楚<br />\n仲要on99等放吾低佢<br />\n<br />\n好委屈"},{"pid":"2ea1081ec13f7b6988b7e35ccf98f809cd316760","tid":388871,"uid":313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"吾"},{"pid":"6da445e79f78afa268526fb084e7b3429d5e1d9d","tid":388871,"uid":13108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"吾你老母咩 吾吾吾"},{"pid":"89d4507051a7ff1414712dd2381e0844e49e1454","tid":388871,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吾你老母咩 吾吾吾</blockquote><br />\n有咩問題😂"},{"pid":"9b2741a2caaca341f201a1e00b7e2e124065c87a","tid":388871,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:50:48.000Z","msg":"新仔啱啱先用連登呀.."},{"pid":"681afdd00d85f1d30b8c64a9e3fc8cdb56e46b72","tid":388871,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"😂"},{"pid":"eddde60a41eeaeee6046f4e979c50b8717d66b85","tid":388871,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"字都未識打學人開post，走啦"},{"pid":"14a059d7c578cc9b1bffab205106c56bc8d1d21a","tid":388871,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"眼見未為真，耳聽未為實。"},{"pid":"e926cb5d51f4def90d6f8ca494bdc9ca19b3e522","tid":388871,"uid":1274,"like":